data.description: Welcome to desirable St. Petersburg, FL! Perfect starter home, investment property, retirement or second home. This spacious 2 bedrooms/1 bathroom/1 car garage home plus a family room that can be converted to a master bedroom and bathroom if you wish, as it has the space to do so. NEW A/C, NO FLOOD ZONE. This home is conveniently located close to everything and is a short drive from famous downtown St. Pete, Florida's beautiful sandy beaches, Tampa International Airport, St. Pete/Clearwater Airport, restaurants, Tyrone Mall and much more . You will love everything this place has to offer. Call today to make this St. Pete house your HOME!
